item.title: Labaratorinis(final)
item.description: Palauk… Jis kazka kepa public String generatePassword() { String password = ""; for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++) { password += (char) (Math.random() * 26 + 97); } int randomCharPosition = (int) (Math.random() * 10); int randomDigitPosition = (int) (Math.random() * 10); password = password.substring(0, randomCharPosition) + (int) (Math.random() * 10) + password.substring(randomCharPosition); password = password.substring(0, randomDigitPosition) + (char) (Math.random() * 26 + 65) + password.substring(randomDigitPosition); return password; }
